<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">السَّابِعَةَ عَشْرَةَ:</span> عُمْقُ عِلْمِ السَّلَفِ؛<span class="c5"> لِقَولِهِ:</span> <span class="c1">"قَدْ أَحْسَنَ مَنِ انْتَهَى إِلَى مَا سَمِعَ؛ وَلَكِنْ كَذَا وَكَذَا"</span>؛ فَعُلِمَ أَنَّ الحَدِيثَ الأَوَّلَ لَا يُخَالِفُ الثَّانِي.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الثَّامِنَةَ عَشْرَةَ:</span> بُعْدُ السَّلَفِ عَنْ مَدْحِ الإِنْسَانِ بِمَا لَيسَ فِيهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">التَّاسِعَةَ عَشْرَةَ:</span> قَولُهُ: <span class="c2">((أَنْتَ مِنْهُمْ)</span>) عَلَمٌ مِنْ أَعْلَامِ النُّبُوَّةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">العِشْرُونَ:</span> فَضِيلَةُ عُكَّاشَةَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الحَادِيَةُ وَالعِشْرُونَ:</span> اسْتِعْمَالُ المَعَارِيضِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">الثَّانِيَةُ وَالعِشْرُونَ:</span> حُسْنُ خُلُقِهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>